title: DFX GOLD Audio Enhancer 12.11.00 DC + Working patch
description:
***************************************************
DFX GOLD Audio Enhancer 12.11.00 DC + Working patch
***************************************************

*** Release date: 15.11.2015

* Compatible With Most Online Music, Video, News and Sports Websites

DFX enhances the sound of most online music and video websites in supported Web browsers, including YouTube, Pandora, Hulu, CNN, ESPN, Last.fm, Vimeo, Dailymotion,Yahoo!, Google+,Google Play, iTunes Movie Trailers, TuneIn, Grooveshark, MOG, VEVO, Rdio, Rhapsody, Flickr, Deezer, Slacker Radio, Jango, Turntable.fm, SoundCloud, Songza, iHeartRadio, SiriusXM Internet Radio, Pitchfork, Blip.tv, and many more.

* Compatible With Most Online Games

DFX enhances the sound of most online gaming websites and web apps in supported Web browsers, including Zynga, Angry Birds, Yahoo! Games, Games.com, Addicting Games, Miniclip, Nickelodeon Games, Shockwave.com, PBS Kids Games, Pogo.com, MSN Games, Disney Games, Cartoon Network Games, PopCap, GameHouse, Big Fish Games, Bigpoint.com, Candystand.com, and many more.

* Compatible With Popular Desktop Media Players and Media Formats

DFX enhances the sound of most popular media players, including iTunes, Spotify, Windows Media Player, Winamp, VLC media player, QuickTime Player, Pandora One Desktop, RealPlayer, Rhapsody Software, Last.fm Scrobbler, JetAudio, GOM Player, MediaMonkey, foobar2000, BS.Player, and JRiver Media Center.

* DFX enhances nearly all downloaded audio formats:
MP3, AAC (M4A), Windows Media (WMA), Real Media (RMJ), Ogg Vorbis (OGG), and WAV.

* DFX also enhances nearly all popular streaming audio formats:
Windows Media, streaming MP3, and RealAudio. That means you can enjoy DFX enhancement with nearly all Internet radio stations including ShoutCast, Live365, SKY.FM, TuneIn, and many others.

* DFX also enhances the audio soundtracks of video formats:
MPEG-4/H.264 (MP4, MOV, M4V), Windows Media, Real Media, Winamp video, and DivX video.

Finally, DFX can even enhance CD playback. 

* System requirements: 32bit/64bit versions of Windows 10, 8/8.1, 7, Vista, XP
